<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ruah channak tha bik, Jesuh kei ca, Pathian sunparnak, Keimah ka tep
 cang, Khamhnak ro cotu Pathian cawk mi, A thi sungbik in a ka tawl cang.

[C1]
   Mah hi ka tuanbia le hla a si, Chun nitlak i Khamhbawi thangthat hi,
   Mah hi ka tuanbia le hla a si, Chun nitlak i khamhbawi thangthat hi.

[V2]
 Amah duhnak zulh, thil nuam bikmi, Lunglawmhnak thlam cu keimah ka
 hmuh cang, Vanmi nih van khin an rung tum i, Dawtnak le vel ngeihnak an
 runpi.

[C2]
   Mah hi ka tuanbia le hla a si, Chun nitlak i Khamhbawi thangthat hi,
   Mah hi ka tuanbia le hla a si, Chun nitlak i khamhbawi thangthat hi.

[V3]
 Amah duhnak zulh, dinhnak a si, Ka Khamhtu sinah keimah ka lawm ko,
 Van khi zoh in ka hngah zungzal i, A thatnak le dawtnak a ka pek.

[C3]
   Mah hi ka tuanbia le hla a si, Chun nitlak i Khamhbawi thangthat hi,
   Mah hi ka tuanbia le hla a si, Chun nitlak i khamhbawi thangthat hi.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>RUAHCHANNAK THA BIK, JESUH KEI CA CH340</title>
